Subject: Tap vs. Drill size chart

Just passing this along... It would be useful to take this chart and  
match it up with specific applications. I have a ton of screws and  
nuts sorted out and I'm not sure I know where they go now. :-)

http://www.newmantools.com/tapdrill.htm

METRIC COARSE SIZES

----------------------------
TAP                 DRILL
SIZE                SIZE
----------------------------
1mm x .25            .75mm
1.1 x .25            .85
1.2 x .25            .95
1.4 x .3            1.1
1.6 x .35           1.25
1.7 x .35           1.3
